window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>Finn Featherstone, once a puny outcast, is now a Champion in training. </b></p> <p>Resting in the baldric across his back is none other than Jigsaw, a magical weapon with untold possibilities. This odd instrument of power is one of the hundreds of swords known as Bizarre Blades, a unique and priceless weapon that Kings have sold their Kingdoms just to obtain. Having been stranded in the freezing woods of Shimoshimo, Finn trains hard day in and day out while trying to survive in the deadly weather. All is going decently until his companion, a black feathered Microraptor with an attitude goes missing. Finn then ventures from the safety of his camp in search of his little friend of which he hears crying out in the night. If only he knew what dangers awaited him in the dark woods. </p> <p>Finn's story is a prequel to The Bizarre Blades series.</p>"; 
